europeana:record.dc:title: On the occurrence of spondylosis deformans in white-beaked dolphins Lagenorhynchus albirostris (Gray, 1846) stranded on the Dutch coast
Zoologische Mededelingen
europeana:record.dc:creator: Kompanje E.J.O.
europeana:record.dc:subject: Mammalia
Spondylosis deformans; Lagenorhynchus albirostris; Cetacea; The Netherlands
europeana:record.dc:description: Fourty-three skeletons of Lagenorhynchus albirostris were examined for the occurrence of pathological changes in the vertebral column. In comparison, 83 skeletons of Phocoena phocoena and 18 of Tursiops truncatus were studied. The pathogenesis of spondylosis deformans is discussed.
